overview:
Your Online Fitness Trainer was created in 2011 by three young entrepreneurs and a team of highly respected fitness experts. They had a vision of using technology to make personal training more flexible, effective, and affordable.

﻿

After much research the Your Online Fitness Trainer team established a partnership with the world leader in online fitness technologies, Hyperstrike. That’s where the YourOnlineFitnessTrainer.com team comes in to use this revolutionary online fitness platform to help you achieve your fitness dreams from around the world.

﻿

Our philosophy: If you don’t exercise you may as well smoke a pack of cigarettes each day, after all, that’s less damaging to your health. Our goal here at YourOnlineFitnessTrainer.com is to stop this sedentary lifestyle that has plagued the western world. Junk food, stress, lack of sleep, and lack of exercise are decimating so many. Our confidence, our energy, our health, and even our lifespan is at risk. Diabetes, obesity, and other degenerative diseases are effecting younger and younger people and health care expenses are going up. What’s the solution? Get in shape! We are all about breaking free from these kinds of lifestyles so that we can be confident, healthy, and not afraid to show off at the beach. That’s why we are prescribing YourOnlineFitnessTrainer.com to YOU.

﻿

www.YourOnlineFitnessTrainer.com provides clients with the most customized and powerful custom workouts, meal plans, fitness assessments, and resource tools in the world. No longer will you be lost at the gym. No longer will you be worried about what you should eat everyday. With our innovative online platform, we will give you step-by-step guidance that makes a difference.
